---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Forward Family Medicine"
  description="Privacy policy for Forward Family Medicine — how we collect, use, and protect your personal information."
>
  <section class="page-hero section" style="background: var(--cream-100);">
    <div class="container">
      <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">Home</a> <span aria-hidden="true">›</span> <span>Privacy Policy</span>
      </nav>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="effective-date">Effective Date: January 1, 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="background: var(--cream-50);">
    <div class="container prose-container">

      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>
        When you submit a form on our website, we may collect personal information including your name, email address, phone number, date of birth, and health-related information submitted through our contact and enrollment forms.
      </p>

      <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>
        We use the information you provide to respond to your inquiries, schedule consultations, and support enrollment in our practice. We do not use your information for marketing purposes beyond direct follow-up related to your inquiry.
      </p>

      <h2>How Your Information Is Transmitted</h2>
      <p>
        Form submissions on this website are sent via a secure Google Apps Script endpoint. Submitted data is not stored on this website. It is transmitted directly to our practice for review and follow-up.
      </p>

      <h2>Third Parties</h2>
      <p>
        We do not sell or share your personal information with third parties, except as required to provide care. For example, once you enroll as a patient, your information will be managed within our electronic health record (EHR) platform, SigmaMD, which maintains its own privacy and security practices.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        If you have questions about this privacy policy or how your information is handled, please contact us at <a href="mailto:information@forwardfamilymedicine.com">information@forwardfamilymedicine.com</a>.
      </p>

    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  .breadcrumb {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--ink-300);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .breadcrumb a { color: var(--green-300); text-decoration: none; }
  .breadcrumb a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

  .page-hero h1 { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }

  .effective-date {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--ink-500);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .prose-container {
    max-width: 720px;
  }
  .prose-container h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--ink-900);
    margin: 2rem 0 0.6rem;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--ink-100);
  }
  .prose-container h2:first-child {
    border-top: none;
    padding-top: 0;
    margin-top: 0;
  }
  .prose-container p {
    color: var(--ink-700);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.97rem;
  }
  .prose-container a {
    color: var(--green-300);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
